high_descs: Walk to the stove, then turn left and face the green island bar.
Pick up the knife on the corner of the bar.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the bar.
Put the knife on the bar.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn to your right and walk to the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the grilling pan on the stove.
Pick up the grilling pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk back to the bar.
Sit the grilling pan on the bar.
anns.task_desc: Put a grilling pan with a slice of tomato on the island bar.

high_descs: Move forward to alongside the chair, turn right, move to past the island edge, turn left, move past the island, turn left, move to alongside the knife on the island, turn left.
Pick up the knife.
Turn right, move to the center of the basin on the right, turn right move to the basin.
Trim and slice the tomato.
Turn left, move to alongside the lettuce on the island, turn left, move to the island.
Place the knife on the island in front of the lettuce.
Turn around, move to the basin.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around, move to alongside the pan on the right burner of the stove, turn left, move to the stove
Put the slice of tomato in the pan.
Pick up the pan.
Turn around, move to the knife on the island, turn left, move to the island
Put the pan on the island to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato in a pan on the island.

high_descs: Head across the room to the dishwasher and turn right after you pass the island, then turn to your right again so that you are facing the center of the island.
Pick up the yellow knife on the kitchen island.
Turn around and go to the kitchen sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink, under the faucet.
Turn around so that you are facing the kitchen island again.
Place the knife on the island, in front of the head of lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the kitchen sink.
Turn to your right and walk to the stove.
Place the slice of tomato on the fry pan, on the front, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the fry pan on the stove containing the tomato slice.
Turn around and walk to the center of the kitchen island, then turn to your right so that you are facing the island.
Place the fry pan with a tomato slice on the edge of the island, closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing a tomato slice on the kitchen island.
